Package org.github.fussel178.telestion.extension.corfu.corfu.mapper.store

Class HashMessageTypeStore

java.lang.Object
org.github.fussel178.telestion.extension.corfu.corfu.mapper.store.HashMessageTypeStore
All Implemented Interfaces:
MessageTypeStore
Direct Known Subclasses:
GlobalStore
public class HashMessageTypeStore extends Object implements MessageTypeStore
A reference implementation for the MessageTypeStore that utilizes HashMaps to store class-id and class-name references for:
  • CorfuNode
  • CorfuAppTelemetry
  • AppTelemetryPayload
  • CorfuAppTelecommand
  • AppTelecommandPayload
